com.saucelabs.ci

Class BrowserFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saucelabs.ci.BrowserFactory

  • public class BrowserFactory
extends Object
    Handles invoking the Sauce REST API to retrieve the list of valid Browsers. The list of browser is cached for an hour.
    Author:
    Ross Rowe
